ZH: 我们经常在周末互相串门。
EN: We often visit each other on weekends.

ZH: 昨天晚上，我串门去朋友家吃晚饭。
EN: Last night, I visited a friend's house for dinner.

ZH: 周末的时候，我特别喜欢串门看朋友。
EN: I love visiting friends on weekends.

ZH: 周日下午，父母串门来我家。
EN: My parents visited my house on Sunday afternoon.

ZH: 周一的时候，同事串门找我讨论工作问题。
EN: On Monday, my colleague visited to discuss work problems.

ZH: 每次节假日，我们都会串门去亲戚家。
EN: Every holiday, we visit relatives' houses.

ZH: 节假日的时候，很多人都会串门拜访亲朋好友。
EN: Many people visit relatives and friends during holidays.

ZH: 春节期间，我们全家都会串门拜年。
EN: During the Spring Festival, our whole family visits relatives' houses to give new year's greetings.

ZH: 每次过生日，朋友们都会串门来给我庆祝。
EN: Every birthday, friends come over to celebrate with me.

ZH: 老师串门家长来开家长会。
EN: Teachers invite parents over for parent-teacher conferences.

ZH: 每年过年，我都会串门亲朋好友家拜年。
EN: Every Chinese New Year, I visit relatives and friends to give new year's greetings.

ZH: 每次过年，我都很期待串门亲戚家。
EN: I always look forward to visiting relatives' houses during the Chinese New Year.

ZH: 每逢大节日，我们家人都要串门亲戚朋友家。
EN: During major holidays, our family visits relatives and friends.

ZH: 节假日的时候，外地亲戚会串门来看我们。
EN: During holidays, relatives from out of town come to visit us.

ZH: 我们串门去表姐家参加她的生日派对。
EN: We visited my cousin's house to attend her birthday party.

ZH: 每次过节，大家都会互相串门拜年。
EN: During each holiday, everyone visits each other to give new year's greetings.

ZH: 今天下午我要串门去看看老同学。
EN: I'm going to visit an old classmate this afternoon.

ZH: 周日的时候，我们全家都会串门去看电影。
EN: On Sundays, our whole family goes to watch movies together.

ZH: 父亲节，我们会串门送礼给爸爸。
EN: On Father's Day, we visit and give gifts to dad.

ZH: 过年期间，爷爷奶奶会串门来跟我们团聚。
EN: During the Lunar New Year, grandparents visit us to reunite.
